A JOINT RESOLUTION
for
1 A JOINT RESOLUTION commemorating the 100th anniversary of
2 Nellie Tayloe Ross becoming the first woman to hold the office
3 of governor in the United States.
4
5 WHEREAS, Nellie Tayloe Ross was born on November 29, 1876, in
6 St. Joseph, Missouri; and
7
8 WHEREAS, after being raised in the great plains and midwest,
9 Nellie Tayloe Ross came to Cheyenne, Wyoming, and married
10 William B. Ross, a lawyer and aspiring politician; and
11
12 WHEREAS, Nellie Tayloe Ross was described as gracious, funny,
13 smart and strongly loyal to her friends and family; and
14
